        return bool(strTemp and not strTemp.isspace())
    else:
        return bool(strValue and not strValue.isspace())

                tempData.append(strvalue)
        else:
            tempData.append(value1)

        vData[toKey] = None
        vData[toKey] = tempData
    #    return vData


def convertToArray(value):
    if not isinstance(value, list):
        value = [value]
    return value

        strTemp = ""
        for strvalue1 in strValue:
            strTemp += strvalue1
        return bool(strTemp and not strTemp.isspace())
    else:
        return bool(strValue and not strValue.isspace())

def convertToArray(value):
